		<summary type="html">&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt; In the spring of 1998, Shaare Zedek's New York-based Women's Division, under the watchful direction of Lee Weinbach, chose me as the recipient of the Maimonides  Award. I knew it was not only for my work at Shaare Zedek but also as a first of many future recognitions of my late father's dreams and aspirations for this wonderful institution.&lt;/font&gt; &lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: left; margin: 0in 0in 0pt&quot; align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal&quot;&gt;</summary>
